            <lg xml:id="TK5">
<l>iruḷcē riruviṉaiyuñ cērā viṟaivaṉ</l>
<l>poruḷcēr pukaḻpurintār māṭṭu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The two-fold deeds that spring from darkness shall not adhere to those who delight in the true praise of God.</l>
            </lg>
